-- Cyprus President to Decide Soon Whether to Run in 2013 Elections
-- B y   P a u l   T u g w e l l
-- 2012-05-13T12:37:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-13/cyprus-president-to-decide-soon-whether-to-run-in-2013-elections.html
Cyprus President Demetris Christofias
will announce in the next few days whether to stand as a
candidate in presidential elections scheduled for 2013.  “You will hear the decision very soon,” Christofias told
reporters in Nicosia today, according to a transcript of his
comment posted on the Cyprus government website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
